{"type":"message","id":"5cb274ec","parentId":"0462c51a","timestamp":"2026-03-03T04:25:49.820Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Good, now I need to update the policy.md with the new decisions. Let me add sections for:\n1. Health check during quiet hours\n2. Error handling\n3. Ops.log retention\n4. Task lists\n\nI'll edit the policy.md to add these.","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"Now updating the policy with your decisions:"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_834bb12453e948468ae3e6a7","name":"edit","arguments":{"file_path":"/root/.openclaw/workspace/system/policy.md","oldText":"## Quiet Hours Rules\n\n- **No outbound messages**\n- **Never modify `user/` or `sources/`**\n- **Internal processing only**\n\n**Split:**\n| Half | Hours (IST) | Focus |\n|------|-------------|-------|\n| First | 00:00–02:30 | Learning + experimentation |\n| Second | 02:30–05:00 | Brief preparation + queue scheduling |","newText":"## Quiet Hours Rules\n\n- **No outbound messages**\n- **Never modify `user/` or `sources/`**\n- **Internal processing only**\n\n**Task Sources:**\n| Scope | File | Pick Method |\n|-------|------|-------------|\n| System-wide | `system/tasks.md` | Round-robin per tick |\n| Channel-specific | `discord/<channel>/tasks.md` | Round-robin per channel visit |\n\n**Split:**\n| Half | Hours (IST) | Focus |\n|------|-------------|-------|\n| First | 00:00–02:30 | Learning + experimentation |\n| Second | 02:30–05:00 | Brief preparation + queue scheduling |\n\n## Health Check (System-Wide)\n\nDuring quiet hours, run health check task periodically:\n\n1. Scan all Discord channels\n2. For each channel without folder structure, create:\n   - `discord/<channel>/purpose.md`\n   - `discord/<channel>/activity.log`\n   - `discord/<channel>/agent/manual.md`\n   - `discord/<channel>/sources/`\n   - `discord/<channel>/user/`\n3. Log creation in `system/ops.log`\n\n## Error Handling\n\nIf channel read/write fails:\n1. Log error in `system/ops.log`\n2. Skip to next channel\n3. No retry same tick (will naturally retry next round-robin)\n\n## Ops.log Retention\n\n- Keep last 30 days\n- Pruned nightly by cron: `scripts/prune-ops-log.sh`\n- Script location: `scripts/` in workspace root"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"zai","model":"glm-5","usage":{"input":972,"output":505,"cacheRead":16704,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":18181,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1772511935026}}
