{"type":"message","id":"ba929c1c","parentId":"a1377ffa","timestamp":"2026-03-03T04:33:40.719Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_83ad87bcd07b49dc803544be","toolName":"exec","content":[{"type":"text","text":"# #bytebles\n\nTeaching channel for Bytebles — Gerson's education brand.\n\n**Offerings:**\n- Group classes\n- Private one-on-one classes\n- Workshops\n\n**Current (March 2026):**\n- Python class (ongoing)\n- Web Design class (ongoing)\n- Workshops coming later this month\n---\n# Knights of St. Joseph\n\n**Catholic Boys Club** based in Goa, started by Gerson a couple years ago.\n\n## Purpose\n- Organizing events\n- Planning events\n- Managing regular group activities and going-ons\n---\n# Santa Casa\n\nCatholic homeschooling coop program based in Goa, started by Stephanie Nazareth and Gerson.\n\n- Regular days: Every Wednesday\n- Location: Goa\n- Founders: Stephanie Nazareth, Gerson\n\n## Channel Use\n\n- Managing coop projects\n- Lesson planning"}],"details":{"status":"completed","exitCode":0,"durationMs":34,"aggregated":"# #bytebles\n\nTeaching channel for Bytebles — Gerson's education brand.\n\n**Offerings:**\n- Group classes\n- Private one-on-one classes\n- Workshops\n\n**Current (March 2026):**\n- Python class (ongoing)\n- Web Design class (ongoing)\n- Workshops coming later this month\n---\n# Knights of St. Joseph\n\n**Catholic Boys Club** based in Goa, started by Gerson a couple years ago.\n\n## Purpose\n- Organizing events\n- Planning events\n- Managing regular group activities and going-ons\n---\n# Santa Casa\n\nCatholic homeschooling coop program based in Goa, started by Stephanie Nazareth and Gerson.\n\n- Regular days: Every Wednesday\n- Location: Goa\n- Founders: Stephanie Nazareth, Gerson\n\n## Channel Use\n\n- Managing coop projects\n- Lesson planning","cwd":"/root/.openclaw/workspace"},"isError":false,"timestamp":1772512420714}}
